        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 pt-4">2. Products and Orders</h2>
        <p>
          We strive to display our products and pricing accurately. We reserve the right to correct errors, limit quantities, and refuse or cancel orders (including after acceptance) in the event of pricing or availability errors, suspected fraud, or for other reasons consistent with good faith business practice. If your order is cancelled after payment, we will refund the amount paid.
        </p>
        <p>
          All orders are subject to acceptance and availability. We will send an order confirmation by email; that email is our acceptance of your order. We do not guarantee that all products shown are in stock at all times.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 pt-4">3. Pricing and Payment</h2>
        <p>
          Prices are in U.S. dollars and do not include applicable taxes or shipping unless stated. You are responsible for any sales tax, VAT, or other taxes that apply to your order. We accept the payment methods displayed at checkout. By providing payment information, you represent that you are authorized to use it. We use third-party payment processors; their terms may also apply.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 pt-4">4. Shipping and Delivery</h2>
        <p>
          Shipping times and costs are estimates and may vary. We are not responsible for delays caused by carriers or events outside our control. Risk of loss and title for items pass to you upon delivery to the carrier. If your order is lost or damaged in transit, please contact us and we will work with you and the carrier to resolve the issue in accordance with our policies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 pt-4">5. Returns and Refunds</h2>
        <p>
          Our return and refund policy is described on the Site (e.g., on product or checkout pages or in a dedicated returns section). Please review that policy before purchasing. Returns must comply with the stated conditions (e.g., time frame, condition of product). Refunds will be processed in accordance with our policy and may take several business days to appear on your statement.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 pt-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The Site and its content (including text, graphics, logos, images, and software) are owned by Bobcat Medical or our licensors and are protected by copyright, trademark, and other laws. You may not copy, modify, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without our prior written permission. "Bobcat Medical" and related marks are our trademarks.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 pt-4">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          The Site and our products are provided "as is" and "as available." We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of harmful components. To the fullest extent permitted by law, we disclaim all warranties, express or implied, including merchantability and fitness for a particular purpose. Our products are intended for general use as medical accessories; they are not medical devices and are not intended to diagnose, treat, or prevent any medical condition. Always follow applicable professional and safety guidelines.
